Subject: From Mono to Poly and Poly/Mono
Description: Exploring polyamory can be a challenge for those new to it. Opening up a monogamous relationship is full of its own set of unique challenges. Discussions on opening up, training wheels for newbies, avoiding pitfalls, as well as dealing with those not avoided. Will also touch on what happens when one partner doesn't want to date others as their partner moves into poly.  Speakers include:Catrice Thornton, Isaac Thornton - Track: Life  - Duration: 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: none
